findAllExtendedGroups

public java.util.Set<java.lang.Class<?>> findAllExtendedGroups(java.util.Collection<java.lang.Class<?>> baseGroups)
                                                        throws java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
Finds all of the validation groups extended by an intial set of groups.

Parameters:
baseGroups - The initial set of groups to find parents of. These groups must have been added to the inheritance map already.
Returns:
A unified set of groups and their parents.
Throws:
java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - If an initial group has not been added to the map before calling this method.

getParentsOfGroup

public java.util.Set<java.lang.Class<?>> getParentsOfGroup(java.lang.Class<?> group)
